QuestionComposite is a CompositeForm
    is primary
    title is "Question"
    context form is QuestionContext
    Question is a Panel
        form is QuestionMain
    YesNoAnswers is a Panel
        visible when (ResponseType.YesNo)
        list is QuestionAnswer set.QuestionYesNoAnswers
    YesNoTextAnswers is a Panel
        visible when (ResponseType.YesNoText)
        list is QuestionAnswer set.QuestionYesNoTextAnswers
    ListAnswers is a Panel
        visible when (ResponseType.List)
        list is QuestionAnswer set.QuestionListAnswers
    RebateAnswers is a Panel
        visible when (ResponseType.Rebate)
        list is QuestionAnswer set.QuestionRebateAnswers
    Terms is a Panel
        visible when (CanAttachTerms)
        list is QuestionAnswerArticleRel.QuestionAnswerArticles
            helper list is ArticleDisplayRel.QuestionArticles
                action is AttachToQuestionOrAnswer
